            "id": "urn:summary_document_report:quartr.com:3672812:0",
            "title": "SIGI: Q2 2026 net income rose 51%, with improved underwriting, strong investments, and $58M returned to shareholders",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-Xl9a4Ubk body-nzzZVyQ3 content-nzzZVyQ3\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-uFduEtAF logosContainer-diQOvrPB\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Q2 2026 saw strong financial performance with a 51% increase in net income, improved combined ratio, and robust investment income. The company returned $58 million to shareholders, renewed key reinsurance treaties, and maintained a strong capital position while navigating competitive and macroeconomic challenges.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Original document: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.tradingview.com/accounts/signin?next=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-mediator.tradingview.com%2Fdoc-screener%2Fv1%2Ffiles%2Furn%3Areport%3Aquartr.com%3A3672812-59e4cbcd459faf1b37a4f3a2af6500d9\" target=\"_blank\">Selective Insurance Group, Inc. [SIGI] SEC 10-Q Quarterly Report — Jul. 24 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-Gmpzg_mv disclaimer-PlF2Sa64\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-Gmpzg_mv\"><span class=\"heading-Gmpzg_mv\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-Gmpzg_mv link-with-underline-Gmpzg_mv\"><span>This is an AI-generated summary and may contain inaccuracies. Please verify any important information with the original source.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
